---

<a
    class=" text-white px-5 py-2 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-lg cursor-pointer select-none fixed z-30 top-1 right-1"
    href={localization_link}
>
    {getLocaleIcon(getLocaleText(locales, "lang_switch_text"))}
